{"tid":267263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"太和邨高空擲屎 19歲青年中招報警","createTime":"2017-06-02T07:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T07:48:30.000Z","uid":94118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6809c139fd76ab5024126b5a3c93506217b1d657","tid":267263,"uid":94118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:07:47.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】大埔太和邨發生高空擲屎！事發今早6時許，19歲姓陳青年在太和邨2期商場對開與友人聊天期間，突有一堆糞便從天而降，擲中青年的褲子上，傳出陣陣異味。青年大驚報警求助，警員到場後，上門逐層搜索惟未有發現。青年事後回家清洗褲子，警方列作雜項案件處理，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7eca56dfc6ca601b33685c29704b2462dfea2b","tid":267263,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚慘"},{"pid":"5dc538170adf31383df449542aa71241c3375d69","tid":267263,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"擺明嘈親啲廢老瞓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5be7f78c0b11c0d18fca8f52733dee1b7e0b41f","tid":267263,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"如果中頭。。。"},{"pid":"3b15c8c258facd470297b86fc2d57499f2886e66","tid":267263,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擺明嘈親啲廢老瞓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘈醒班廢老起身晨運仲好喇<br />\n唔係佢地一陣點同打工仔學生爭巴士坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f4c60d5f0d9a2ea60ea0d06299c25291a0f770","tid":267263,"uid":25133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07: